name: Membot
description: What is the project about? Membot is a lightning fast Discord based Ethereum wallet, sniper & trading bot. Tokenomics Supply: 1,000,000,000 Max Wallet: 2.5% of total Supply Max Transaction: 1.0% of total Supply Taxes Each Transaction has a 5% Buy & 5% Sales tax. 4% for the Membot Buffer Contract(Used to route ETH to Treasury & Revenue Share Contract) 4% for the Membot Buffer Contract(Used to route ETH to Treasury & Revenue Share Contract) 70% -> Treasury, 30% -> Revenue Share Contract 1% for Liquidity (For adding depth to our liquidity pool) Revenue Share 30% of the taxes collected by the Membot Buffer smart contract will go to our revenue sharing contract for wallets that hold 10,000 $MEMBOT or more. Rewards are funded by 1.2% of all total volume traded on $MEMBOT as well as 50% of Bot transaction fees. All rewards via the Revenue Share Contract will be sent in Ethereum from Disperse.app
